{"title":"Radar Roundup: Shovel Research Goes Gold, Tunitas Motion Camera Strap, DSPTCH and Engineered Garments, Bookman Lights, NPR on NM Outdoor Rec/Mineral Extraction, and Paul’s Pro Cruiser Got Restored","link":"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-shovel-research-goes-gold-tunitas-motion-camera-strap-dsptch-and-engineered-garments-bookman-lights-npr-on-nm-outdoor-rec-mineral-extraction-and-pauls-pro-cruiser-got-restored/","date":1696340812000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?w=1620&amp;quality=75 1620w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></a></p>\n<p>Our Radar Roundup compiles products and videos from the ‘net in an easy-to-digest format. Read on below for today’s findings…<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/gold-hoverover.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/gold-hoverover.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/gold-hoverover.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/gold-hoverover.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/gold-hoverover.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/gold-hoverover.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/gold-hoverover.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/gold-hoverover.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://shovelresearch.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Shovel Research Offers Gold (Finishes)</a></h3>\n<p>Gold anodizing used to be a much bigger thing than it is today with all the major component manufacturers offering this blingy hue as an option: MKS, Ukai, Suntour, and Sugino all made gold anodized components in the late 70s and throughout the 1980s. Shovel Research began offering a beautiful gold finish for its <a href=\"https://shovelresearch.com/fork-mounted-brake-cable-hanger\">FMBCH</a> and light mount. Roll on over to <a href=\"https://shovelresearch.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Shovel Research</a> to check out the offerings.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d79a2be2061547caab4719edd.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d79a2be2061547caab4719edd.jpg?w=1500&amp;quality=75 1500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d79a2be2061547caab4719edd.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d79a2be2061547caab4719edd.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d79a2be2061547caab4719edd.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d79a2be2061547caab4719edd.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d593c8b1e639469f87a40a2c2.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d593c8b1e639469f87a40a2c2.jpg?w=1500&amp;quality=75 1500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d593c8b1e639469f87a40a2c2.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d593c8b1e639469f87a40a2c2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d593c8b1e639469f87a40a2c2.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/d95842_d593c8b1e639469f87a40a2c2.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.tunitascreative.com/product-page/motion-camera-strap\" target=\"_blank\">Tunitas the Makers In Motion Camera Strap</a> $70</h3>\n<p>After a two-year hiatus, Tunitas brought back the Makers In Motion Camera Strap. Now dubbed the Motion Camera Strap, the unique design features a seamlessly integrated stability strap that allows for converting through a two-point strap into a three-point strap and shoot modes quickly. Never miss that perfect shot ever again.</p>\n<p><em>Preorder starts Friday September 29th 7:30am PST and ends Friday October 13th 5:00pm PST. This batch has a 250 unit limit, and the preorder will close early if the limit is met. </em></p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Weight: 89g</li>\n<li>Converts from three-point harness to two-point strap in one seamless motion.</li>\n<li>Adjustable length to achieve the perfect fit.</li>\n<li>Nylon seatbelt webbing provides comfort and durability</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://www.tunitascreative.com/product-page/motion-camera-strap\" target=\"_blank\">Tunitas</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\