pg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/PCK-UVP-EG-GRN-A_1512x.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/PCK-UVP-EG-GRN-A_1512x.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/PCK-UVP-EG-GRN-A_1512x.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/PCK-UVP-EG-GRN-A_1512x.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.dsptch.com/collections/dsptch-x-engineered-garments\" target=\"_blank\">DSPTCH and Engineered Garments</a></h3>\n<p>While considerably more high-end than our typical Roundup fodder, these products from DSPTCH and Engineered Garments are too good to not share. Featuring ultralight Dyneema construction in three dyed color options, in a variety of silhouettes these totes, backpacks, and cross-body bags are made in the USA in small batches and are built to last. There are too many specs and details for each, so check out the full collection at <a href=\"https://www.dsptch.com/collections/dsptch-x-engineered-garments\" target=\"_blank\">DSPTCH</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-1500_black_persputanpower.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-1500_black_persputanpower.jpg?w=1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-1500_black_persputanpower.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-1500_black_persputanpower.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-1500_black_persputanpower.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-1500_black_persputanpower.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-1500_black_persputanpower.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-1500_black_persputanpower.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_white_persputanpowerb.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_white_persputanpowerb.jpg?w=1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_white_persputanpowerb.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_white_persputanpowerb.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_white_persputanpowerb.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_white_persputanpowerb.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_white_persputanpowerb.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_white_persputanpowerb.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_orange_persp-utanpowe.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_orange_persp-utanpowe.jpg?w=1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_orange_persp-utanpowe.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_orange_persp-utanpowe.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_orange_persp-utanpowe.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_orange_persp-utanpowe.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_orange_persp-utanpowe.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/volume-800_orange_persp-utanpowe.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://bookmanvisibility.com/en-us/collections/bike-lights\" target=\"_blank\">Bookman 1500 and 800 Lumen Volume Lights</a> $160/$106</h3>\n<p>The Swedish company, Bookman, has launched two new powerful bike light that sets them apart from the crowd with an innovative mode of operation. Inspired by the Hi-Fi world, the Volume lights are operated by a unique Power Wheel (patent pending), making it conveniently easy to adjust the brightness into one of the five levels. The Volume bike light comes in 800 or 1500 lumens, feature high-output batteries, and come in a bomber aluminum body.</p>\n<p>Check out the full offering at <a href=\"https://bookmanvisibility.com/en-us/collections/bike-lights\" target=\"_blank\">Bookman</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/img_5704-e87ac39c5d5a3ca41204116.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/img_5704-e87ac39c5d5a3ca41204116.jpg?w=1600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/img_5704-e87ac39c5d5a3ca41204116.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/img_5704-e87ac39c5d5a3ca41204116.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/img_5704-e87ac39c5d5a3ca41204116.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/img_5704-e87ac39c5d5a3ca41204116.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/img_5704-e87ac39c5d5a3ca41204116.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2023/09/28/1202187607/fossil-fuel-blm-new-mexico-outdoor-recreation-biden-federal-land-oil-gas\" target=\"_blank\">Western Towns Between Old Economies and New Green Goals</a></h3>\n<p>Like many Western States, New Mexico is battling against the extraction industry by leveraging its outdoor recreation potential. <a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2023/09/28/1202187607/fossil-fuel-blm-new-mexico-outdoor-recreation-biden-federal-land-oil-gas\" target=\"_blank\">NPR’s story on Farmington</a> is worth the read if you follow these conversations closely…</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><span><span>﻿</span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uZGRuN_LxJg\" target=\"_blank\"> Paul’s Pro Cruiser Got Restored<br />\n</a></h3>\n<p>If you’re a fan of vintage mountain bikes but never heard of Pro Cruiser, well, pull up a chair this morning and check out Paul’s freshly restored build!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Radavision</h3>\n<p>Stuff we see on the ‘net that causes pause…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?w=1620&amp;quality=75 1620w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/385751364_1487836685317298_8166643988880914901_n.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Illustration by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Cx7KD7Po1cP/\" target=\"_blank\">@atlasducycle<br />\n</a></em></p>\n<p>We love a good pen and ink drawing and Atlas Du Cycle’s 0.1 ink pen drawing really caught out eyes!</p>\n<p><em>If you’d like your photo featured in our Radar Roundup posts, tag us <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theradavist/\" target=\"_blank\">on Instagram</a>!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-shovel-research-goes-gold-tunitas-motion-camera-strap-dsptch-and-engineered-garments-bookman-lights-npr-on-nm-outdoor-rec-mineral-extraction-and-pauls-pro-cruiser-got-restored/\">Radar Roundup: Shovel Research Goes Gold, Tunitas Motion Camera Strap, DSPTCH and Engineered Garments, Bookman Lights, NPR on NM Outdoor Rec/Mineral Extraction, and Paul’s Pro Cruiser Got Restored</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"56bf906d49a410a26437db84a82e73bb78c54fafc718d4acfe1403df247af805","category":"Cycling"}